name: Terema
overview:
Web-based property management software that allows real estate managers, owners, and vendors to work together to manage their business.

Our online property management software includes powerful and flexible property management functions, a full-featured accounting system, the ability to email owner statements, and share real-time data between owners, managers, and vendors. Advanced budgeting, one-click receivable and payable processing, flexible reporting, and the ability to post ads on the internet are all included.
